editeur.model.menu.EditMenu

Interface EditMenuBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditMenuBuilderJavaFx

    public interface EditMenuBuilder
    The interface EditMenuBuilder represents the steps for building a Editmenu. Some steps can not be done. Once all the step you need are done you can build the result. Can have multiple Representations.
